reviewText: Worst movie ever .. not even funny
Wanted more, but was OK? A bit Corny. lol

Like the movie.  The Mockumentary of Cornhole was  the idea of this movie.  Only problem had to many story lines could have got rid of two and focused own the others.  But If you like playing Cornhole and like ok movies get. But if those things don't apply to you don't get.

The Movie is a mockumentary feature film that examines the lives of four groups of quirky characters who have sacrificed, exploited, and shamed those in their lives to gain a certain level of minimal fame in the Cincinnati based sport of Cornhole.

Although I did recieve the DVD very quickly, it was so scratched up that it was unplayable. I notified the company the next day but after 3 weeks I still haven't recieved word back. I have bought many things through Amazon, and until this purchase I have always been happy with the quality and fast delivery.
